<HEAD>Jeffords Poised to Move to Senate, Sanders Bidding for House Seat</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MONTPELIER, Vt. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Republican Rep. James Jeffords was
expected to claim the seat of retiring Sen. Robert Stafford on
